### ========================================
### 00 - Health Check & Public Endpoints
### ========================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081/api

### Ping - verify server is alive

GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/ping
Accept: application/json

### Health endpoint (Actuator)
# Note: Actuator runs at root context, not under /api
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### API Docs (OpenAPI JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api-docs
Accept: application/json

### Swagger UI (redirects to full UI page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger-ui.html
Accept: text/html

### ========================================
### Public Content
### ========================================

### List public services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
Accept: application/json

### List public articles
GET {{baseUrl}}/articles
Accept: application/json

### List public testimonials
GET {{baseUrl}}/testimonials
Accept: application/json
